quran[9]{c,v,t,f}:
  26,61,"Basi ndema jagaonegene makuga ganagaŵili (likuga lya Firiauna ni lya Musa), ŵandu ŵa Musa ŵatite: “Chisimu uwwe chitukamulwe.”"
  26,62,"Jwalakwe jwatite: “Ngwamba! Chisimu Ambuje ŵangu ali none, chanjongolele (yakutenda kuti mpaka tujokoche).”"
  26,63,"Basi ni twan’juwulile Musa (maloŵe ganti): “Putani mbwani ni simbo jenujo.” Ni jagaŵanyiche, upande uliose waliji nti chisawu litumbi lyekulungwa."
  27,34,"(Nyakongwe) ŵatite: “Chisimu achiŵenye naga ali aujinjile musi, akasaujonangaga ni kwatenda ŵakuchimbichika mwa ŵandu ŵakwe kuŵa ŵakunyosyeka, mwele ni mwaakasatendela (ndema syose).”"
  27,35,"“Basi chisimu une chindumisye kukwao ntuuka, basi ninole kuti ana tisiuje nayo yantiuli ndumetume.”"
  27,36,"Basi ndema jasyaiche (ndumetume sila) kwa Sulaimana, jwalakwe jwatite: “Ana nkungamuchisya ni chipanje? Yambele une Allah ili yambone nnope kupunda yampele ŵanganyammwe, nambo kuti jenumanja nkuchina ni ntuuka wenu.”"
  28,7,"Ni twan’juwulile mamagwe Musa yanti: “Mun’jonjesyeje jwalakwe (Musa). Nambo naga mun’jogopele (kuti atakwisa mwankopocheele Firiauna), basi mumponye nnusulo; nkajogopa soni nkadandaula, chisimu Uwwe chitum’buchisye jwalakwe kukwenu, ni kwisa kuntenda kuŵa mwa achimitenga.”"
  28,8,"Basi ni ŵannokwete ŵandu ŵa Firiauna kuti chasyuche kuŵa mmagongo jwao ni chakudandaulisya chao. Chisimu Firiauna ni Hamana kwisa soni asilikali ŵao ŵaliji ŵakulemwa."
  28,9,"Ŵankwao Firiauna ni ŵatite: “Chakuteteŵalila liso lyangune ni lyenumwe! Nkam’bulaga jwalakweju mwine kuŵa nkutukamuchisya, kapena tugambe kuntenda kuŵa mwana (gwetu).” Ni (ŵatesile yalakweyi) ŵanganyao akakumanyilila (yakuichisya yakwe)."